    "story": "A boy named Buzz wanted a pet for The Amazing Pet Show. He caught a fly in a jar. Everyone said flies can't be pets, they are pests! But this fly was special - he was very smart and could say Buzz's name. The fly also did fancy flying tricks. When the judges saw this, they were amazed. The fly knew his jar and flew back into it. The judges said, 'This fly is a pet!' Buzz named him Fly Guy. And so began a beautiful friendship between a boy and his fly."
